extendedInfo.description: â9 Behaviour issues and METHODS â9 Training guides and SOLUTIONS â9 Tricks topics and step-by-step GUIDESâGold, silver and bronze TESTâAudio book optionFetch isn't your ordinary and boring dog training guide, it's written by professional dog trainers exclusively for this app.Inside this edition there are 27 different dog training topics which range from common dog behaviour issues to training guides and even a selection of amazing tricks to teach your dog that will impress your friends.All 27 training topics have their own set of questions with a Gold, Silver or Bronze medal to be won which will help to reinforce your knowledge and remember the things you have learnt.All of the content can be read to you if you choose by the click of a button, turning this into an audio book.HOW TO USEEverything is designed to be user-friendly. Choose between the behaviour, training and tricks sections by swiping right to left. Once open, click on the topic you wish to read. The text size is adjustable by using the -A and A+ buttons in the bottom right corner. The "Speech" button will turn the text into an audio book and the content will be read out to you. Once you are confident you have absorbed all of the knowledge click on the "Take Test" button which will take you in to quiz in which you can earn gold, silver and bronze medals.NOTE:This app IS suitable for training both puppies and adult dogs.kw: games, ceaser milan, rspca, dogs trust, aspca, german shepherd, pitbull, lead, pulling, sexual maturity, neutering, breeds

reviews.title: Amazing. Thank you!
reviews.comment: We were seriously considering giving up our out of control dog before getting this app. She was trained in 1 afternoon. Sorry i mean we were trained in 1 afternoon as it was more about teaching us than her. She had done nothing wrong it was us not training her properly that caused the behavior issues. Thank you so much.
reviews.author: Emma Rush

reviews.title: Locked status after buying the entire package.
reviews.comment: Hi developer, I am impressed with your training guidelines. They work wonders. I had bought the entire package and all the locked icons disappeared. But after few days, the lock appears again. What is this all about? I am not happy with this.
